    "description": "Help Mr. Mookie retrieve his giant cookie in this adorable puzzle-platformer! Glide through the clouds, explore alien lands, and solve complex puzzles to get the cookie and dip it in milk.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404060/extras/a8deaba0a10a2946cf662d00961ba93d.poster.avif?t=1707542106\" width=480 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404060/extras/a8deaba0a10a2946cf662d00961ba93d.webm?t=1707542106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404060/extras/a8deaba0a10a2946cf662d00961ba93d.mp4?t=1707542106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore Different Lands</h2><br>Explore five different environments ranging from a cheery, lively playground to a dark, creepy factory as you try to recapture your cookie!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404060/extras/9b88bb6493b2ea0505583736bd7afeff.poster.avif?t=1707542106\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404060/extras/9b88bb6493b2ea0505583736bd7afeff.webm?t=1707542106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404060/extras/9b88bb6493b2ea0505583736bd7afeff.mp4?t=1707542106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve Complex Puzzles</h2><br>Each of the five chapters has 20 unique, hand-crafted levels, from simple relaxing ones to complex head-scratchers, giving you a wide range of puzzles to complete.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404060/extras/ef325ab0fd28b8a25b03b5df375ce076.poster.avif?t=1707542106\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404060/extras/ef325ab0fd28b8a25b03b5df375ce076.webm?t=1707542106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404060/extras/ef325ab0fd28b8a25b03b5df375ce076.mp4?t=1707542106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Pickups that Alter Gameplay</h2><br>Catapult a cookie over castle towers, glide through the clouds with a hang glider, and skyrocket with a jetpack in the factory. Each of the five chapters has different pickups that change how you play the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404060/extras/d5f7d83dfcac01e6df68f87c4def5190.poster.avif?t=1707542106\" width=480 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404060/extras/d5f7d83dfcac01e6df68f87c4def5190.webm?t=1707542106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404060/extras/d5f7d83dfcac01e6df68f87c4def5190.mp4?t=1707542106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Puzzles:</strong> Explore 100 hand-crafted levels spread out across five different chapters</li><li><strong>Increasingly Difficult Puzzles:</strong> Each of the levels contains puzzles, ranging from simple relaxing ones to complex head-scratchers </li><li><strong>Mechanics Build:</strong> New mechanics start off easy in earlier levels, then get increasingly difficult, letting you master the different elements of the game </li><li><strong>Unique Pickups:</strong> Each chapter contains their own pickups, like jetpacks, a hang glider, and even a watering can, each one altering the gameplay</li></ul>",
